articles.title: UK home secretary signs new asylum treaty in Rwanda - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: James Cleverly visits Rwanda after a UK court ruling declared a deportation scheme to the East African nation illegal.
articles.content:
British Home Secretary James Cleverly has signed a new treaty to send asylum seekers to Rwanda after the United Kingdoms top court declared the deportation scheme unlawful.
